  "title": "Permanent Baseload Maintenance Engineer at Ang Mo Kio, Up to $6,000 + VB (Office hours)",
  "description": "<p><strong>- Permanent</strong></p><p><strong>- Up to $6,000 + VB</strong></p><p><strong>- Mon – Fri: 8.30am – 5.30pm</strong></p><p><strong>- Ang Mo Kio</strong><br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>We are looking for a BMS Engineer (Technical Team) to be part of a team in supporting and keeping our customer’s systems up and running smoothly.</p><ul><li><p>Infrastructure : system patching, troubleshoot infrastructure issues and setup/reinstall of servers/workstations</p></li><li><p>Security : VAPT (Vulnerability Assessment & Penetration Testing) support, VAPT remediation support and compliance support</p></li><li><p>Operating System : Windows Server 2022 & Above, Windows 11 and RHEL 8 & Above</p></li><li><p>Products : Fortinet (ForitManager, Firewall), Cisco Router and Switches and Security Products (Splunk, Trellix, Cyberark, IBM Guardian)</p></li><li><p>Compliances : CIS Benchmark, CCOP (Cybersecurity Code of Practice by CSA) and IM8 Policies</p></li><li><p>Others : project audit support, incident support (Infrastructure, Network, Security), annual DR support and ad-Hoc Network Issue Support</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Period:</strong></p><ul><li>Permanent<br /><br /></li></ul><p><strong>Location:</strong></p><ul><li>Ang Mo Kio</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Working hours:</strong></p><ul><li>Mon – Fri: 8.30am – 5.30pm</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Salary:</strong></p><ul><li>Up to $6,000 + VB</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma in Computer Science / Information Technology / Cybersecurity or equivalent</p></li><li><p>Minimum 2 years of relevant working experience in IT Network, Systems & Security administration</p></li></ul><p></p><p>Interested applicants, kindly email your detailed resume (<strong>MS Word </strong>format is preferred):</p><p><strong>joan@successhrc.com.sg </strong>(Reg No: <strong>R1332758</strong>)</p><p>Please ensure that applications sent through email are <strong>no bigger than 1Mb</strong>.</p><p>We thank all applicants for your interest but regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified.<br /></p><p><strong>Success Human Resource Centre Pte Ltd</strong> (EA License Number: <strong>97C4832</strong>)</p><p>160 Robinson Road, #13-07/08/09 SBF Center, Singapore 068914<br />T: 6337 3183 | W: <a href=\"http://www.successhrc.com.sg/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.successhrc.com.sg</a> </p>",
